.PrettyPrinter.combinatorFormatterAttribute\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">combinatorFormatterAttribute</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/ParserCompiler/Attribute.html#Lean.ParserCompiler.CombinatorAttribute\">ParserCompiler.CombinatorAttribute</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.lean#L65-L89","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.formatterAttribute","line":65,"kind":"opaque","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.formatterAttribute","doc":"Registers a formatter for a parser.\n\n`@[formatter k]` registers a declaration of type `Lean.PrettyPrinter.Formatter` to be used for\nformatting syntax of kind `k`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.formatterAttribute\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">PrettyPrinter</span>.<span class=\"name\">formatterAttribute</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/KeyedDeclsAttribute.html#Lean.KeyedDeclsAttribute\">KeyedDeclsAttribute</a> <a href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Formatter\">Formatter</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.lean#L63-L63","name":"Lean.PrettyPrinter.Formatter","line":63,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.Formatter","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/PrettyPrinter/Formatter.html#Lean.PrettyPrinter.F